    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ADD
      Adds (or subtracts) its amount to the base value of the attribute.
      + +
      MULTIPLY
      Sums all amount of modifiers which has this operation, and calls as x.
      After that multiplies the base value of the attribute with (x + 1).
      MULTIPLY_ALL
      For every modifier which has this operation, sums by (x + 1) where x is the amount of that modifier.
      After that multiplies each those results together and also multiplies with the base value of the
      attribute.
